    <stitle>ANTILOCK BRAKES/TRACTION CONTROL: ROCKWELL WABCO 4 CHANNEL - INSTALL - ABS VALVE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="1">
        <title>ABS VALVE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Mount the valve with fasteners removed in REMOVE. Tighten to 18 ft-lbs. (24 N&#8226;m) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0403617">Figure 17</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f0403617" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g0403617" filename="../figg04/G0403617.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 17. ABS Mounted Valve With Fasteners Removed</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect the air line going to the brake chamber to port 2 of the valve and the air supply
                line to port 1 of the valve.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect the harness connector to the valve.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
